txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Albino skin from the beasts and worms near Gath Forthnír. Delivery of the items should be made to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-outpost.
'We can use the skin from beasts and other foul things around to patch holes in many items in the camp. If you can deliver them, we will use them.'
Council of the North Task: Albino Skin
The Rangers at Gath Forthnír await a delivery of albino skin to be made to Areneth.
Deliver the albino skin to Areneth at Gath Forthnír in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver albino skin from the beasts near Gath Forthnír to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-camp.
Wanted: Albino skin from the beasts and worms near Gath Forthnír.
